Serpentor cursed, falling back from shots that pierced into his shoulder.  
Raising his plasma launcher, he fired a blast off at Striker's chest, 
bringing up a laser pistol in his left arm to fire two bolts at Striker's 
left foot, a blast hitting Serpentor in the left knee, causing him to fall to 
his right knee in pain.
